Module 50 – Amicus Engine: From Archive to Brief ⚖️🧩
⚖️ Core Message
Amicus support grows from a clean archive. Offer a brief kit: issue framing, record pin‑cites, and draftable sections the ally can adapt.

📖 Lesson Content
