Module 94 – Privacy Escalation: When to Seal, When to Publish 🌗🔏
⚖️ Core Message
Balance transparency with safety. Use a clear decision tree to decide when to keep items restricted, when to seek sealing, and when to publish.

📖 Lesson Content
• Decision Tree — Risk categories; public interest; availability elsewhere; consent.
• Temporary Seals — Time‑box; periodic review.
• Redaction First — Prefer narrow redactions to full seal.
• Advisory — Consult counsel/ethics when in doubt.
• Logging — Keep a privacy decision log with reasons.
