Module 98 – Open Dataset Release: Licenses, Readmes, and Limits 📂🔓
⚖️ Core Message
If you publish data, publish responsibly: explain scope, methods, and limits; pick a license; and invite replication.

📖 Lesson Content
• License — Open data license with attribution; exclude restricted items.
• README — Scope, definitions, methods, limitations, contact.
• Versioning — Tag releases; keep changelog.
• Consent — Remove PII/PHI; log removals.
• Cite — Provide a preferred citation for reuse.
📝 Assignment
